Agile
Agile is an approach to managing and working on projects.
Agile techniques can also be used to manage service tickets.
Agile projects are iterative
Based on continuous learning and improved iterations(loops/cycles)
It is a mindset and frameworks like Kanban,Scrum,XP etc. are ways to achieve agility

Jira
Atlassian Jira as a tool to help work with Agile processes
It is used to help manage, develop, and communicate about projects

Jira Hierarchy
Application Level->Individual Project Level->Issues/Work Item->
